{"tid":859882,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"關節係運動員既天敵 ［有冇得搞］","createTime":"2018-10-13T01:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T15:56:44.000Z","uid":191993,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9b55d1efaa467ad547c4ffb5c7e4e0fd6c41a3b9","tid":859882,"uid":191993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:54:02.000Z","msg":"天生關節唔好，好多動作個d手腳都會啪啪聲。舉鐵做三頭好多動作都會有聲同痛，平時跳繩平均一次跳20-30分鐘到，但係成日個人未累膝頭就開始痛，以前跑步又係咁，一個鐘到就痛，好多運動都有改過動作，但係都無咩用。有冇巴絲打有相同經驗幫下手？七海健樂有冇用？<br />\n<br />\n我好鐘意做運動同埋想做多d運動keep下fit唔想做大肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c62771a1c5a54e6ae6bbb09d04cced55c3bba56","tid":859882,"uid":191993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T02:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bad51b410c8687a53fc4cc3da9a4a0ca9f9ff0","tid":859882,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T02:04:59.000Z","msg":"你幾重？"},{"pid":"12915e1a9669fee64bbf391355cbf969fc96b804","tid":859882,"uid":191993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T02:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3662e0b176162b2d2c61238ef8caa530529482","tid":859882,"uid":191993,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"c7bad51b410c8687a53fc4cc3da9a4a0ca9f9ff0","tid":859882,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T02:04:59.000Z","msg":"你幾重？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T02:07:45.000Z","msg":"185 90kg<br />\n<br />\n最近無check體脂，但唔算太肥，有做開gym"},{"pid":"03ef4b65162a65ce26adb7fcf63a15b657ab3e13","tid":859882,"uid":140604,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"8d3662e0b176162b2d2c61238ef8caa530529482","tid":859882,"uid":191993,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"quote":{"pi